featuredListings.title: Luxury House in LA
featuredListings.description: Stunning modern luxury home in the heart of Los Angeles featuring 5 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, a gourmet kitchen, infinity pool, and panoramic city views. The property includes smart home technology throughout and a rooftop terrace perfect for entertaining.

featuredListings.title: Modern Apartment in NY
featuredListings.description: Sophisticated 2-bedroom apartment in Manhattan with floor-to-ceiling windows offering breathtaking city views. Features include hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, concierge service, and access to building amenities including fitness center and rooftop lounge.

featuredListings.title: Cozy Condo in SF
featuredListings.description: Charming 2-bedroom condo in a prime San Francisco location. This sun-filled unit features an open floor plan, updated kitchen with quartz countertops, in-unit laundry, and a private balcony. Walking distance to restaurants and public transportation.

featuredListings.title: Beach House in Miami
featuredListings.description: Stunning beachfront property with direct ocean access. This 3-bedroom home features a chef's kitchen, spacious outdoor living area with pool, and private beach access. Large windows throughout provide spectacular water views from every room.

savedProperties.title: Modern Condo in Seattle
savedProperties.description: Contemporary 2-bedroom condo in downtown Seattle with panoramic views of Puget Sound. Features include an open floor plan, gourmet kitchen, floor-to-ceiling windows, and access to building amenities including fitness center and rooftop terrace.

savedProperties.title: Villa in San Diego
savedProperties.description: Stunning Spanish-style villa with 4 bedrooms and a private courtyard. Features include vaulted ceilings, chef's kitchen, solar-heated pool, and mature landscaping. Located in a quiet neighborhood just minutes from the beach.

savedProperties.title: Downtown Apartment in Austin
savedProperties.description: Stylish 1-bedroom apartment in the heart of Austin. Features include hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, walk-in closet, and balcony with downtown views. Building offers pool, fitness center, and is walking distance to entertainment.

savedProperties.title: Cozy Condo in Denver
savedProperties.description: Charming 2-bedroom condo in a historic Denver building. Features include exposed brick walls, updated kitchen, in-unit laundry, and private balcony. Located in a vibrant neighborhood close to restaurants and parks.

propertiesViewed.title: Seaside Condo in Charleston
propertiesViewed.description: Beautiful 3-bedroom oceanfront condo with panoramic water views. Features include a gourmet kitchen, spacious master suite, and private balcony. Building offers pool, beach access, and boat storage.

propertiesViewed.title: Luxury House in Las Vegas
propertiesViewed.description: Spectacular 5-bedroom home in exclusive Summerlin community. Features include a resort-style backyard with pool and cabana, home theater, game room, and mountain views. Close to top golf courses and shopping.

favoriteProperties.title: Lakeside View House in Alaska
favoriteProperties.description: Stunning lakeside property with panoramic views of the Alaskan wilderness. This 4-bedroom home features a spacious deck, wood-fired sauna, and direct access to fishing and kayaking. Perfect for nature lovers seeking tranquility.

favoriteProperties.title: Modern Condo in New York
favoriteProperties.description: Luxury condo in the heart of Manhattan with floor-to-ceiling windows offering city views. Amenities include 24/7 concierge, fitness center, and rooftop lounge. Close to Central Park and top restaurants.

favoriteProperties.title: Penthouse in Pennsylvania
favoriteProperties.description: Elegant penthouse with private elevator access and 360-degree skyline views. Features chef's kitchen, home office, and spa-like master bath. Located in Philadelphia's most prestigious neighborhood.
